color.description: The color of the switch is the same as the color of the css
color.description_zh: switch 的颜色，同 css 的 color

nativeProps.description_zh: 用于透传 WebComponents 上的属性到内部 H5 标签上

name.description: The name of the component, which is used to obtain data for form submission.

controlled.description: Whether it is a controlled component or not, if true, checked is fully controlled by setData.
controlled.description_zh: 是否为受控组件，为 true 时，checked 会完全受 setData 控制。

ariaLabel.description_zh: 无障碍访问，（属性）元素的额外描述

onChange.description: checked 改变时触发 change 事件
onChange.description_zh: checked 改变时触发 change 事件
